<li aria-level="2">End: Fn + Right arrow</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li aria-level="1">Excel (For Apple Extended Keyboard and for MacBook keyboard)
<ul>
<li aria-level="2">Home or Fn + Left arrow: Move to 1st column of current row</li>
<li aria-level="2">Control + Home or Control + Fn + Left arrow: Move to top left cell of the sheet</li>
<li aria-level="2">Control + End or Fn + Control + Right arrow: Move to the last cell in use on the sheet</li>
</ul>
